Author: Bitsbytes
Title: [ANN] Arena - Cryptocurrency Social Network v.1 Alpha Release
Body: Arena is now trading on Forked Delta https://forkdelta.github.io/#!/trade/ARENA-ETH  We are testing the platform and we got the Arena payment gateway to work with Meta Mask. All Arena coins sent on our platform will be sent p2p with no middleman.  We will have a demo as soon as the payment gateway is completed. We will be launching a small marketplace where we will be selling various crypto trading tools for Arena tokens. Soon other members will be able to accept Arena tokens on there profiles for selling trading tips and esports and sports picks! Additional features are being added to the platform.  To keep updated on our progress please visit our Twitter here  https://twitter.com/ArenaPlatform

Author: Bitsbytes
Title: [ANN] Arena - Cryptocurrency Social Network v.1 Alpha Release
Body: The payment gateway is almost done. As you can see here we made it so Arena can accept both Arena tokens and Ethereum tokens. The payment gateway will likely be completed in 1 to 2 weeks. Shortly after the gateway is completed we will open the Alpha version of the site so everyone can test the platform.  https://imgur.com/a/3sAii  Token Fees  Ethereum transaction will have a small Arena token fee to process each transactions. This is similar to other platforms.  All Arena token transfers will have just the gas fee that is standard with all ERC20 token transfers.  We are working on adding more payment options on the Arena platform.  Each member on the platform will have the ability to accept Ethereum and Arena payments for Poker Staking and selling Sports Picks and Trading Picks. Each members just needs to input there payment address and thats it and all transactions will go to your Ethereum address.  To use the platform you must have some Arena tokens, Arena tokens will be used for transaction fees. Arena tokens are traded here:    https://forkdelta.github.io/#!/trade/ARENA-ETH  The Alpha version of the Arena platform will be launching soon. Please stay subscribe to this thread for recent updates. We will also be posting updates on our website.        For recent updates please visit https://projectarena.io/blog

Author: Bitsbytes
Title: [ANN] Arena - Cryptocurrency Social Network v.1 Alpha Release
Body: Arena ICO Ends In 24 hours. All participants will be paid via an airdrop within 24 to 48 hours after the completion of the ICO.        Here are instructions for withdrawing your purchased tokens;  Withdrawal Instructions  You can keep your tokens on the site and withdraw at a later date or withdraw your tokens to a Waves address.  To withdraw your tokens please email us the following;  Send email from: Send us a withdraw request from the email address you used to order tokens.  Send to: Send your withdraw request to withdraw@projectarena.io (Make sure you send from the email address you used when purchasing the tokens)  Email title: Put your total balance in your email title. Example, Withdraw 1000 tokens  Email body: Include your email address used when making the token purchase, order number or numbers and total balance. (Don't put a partial balance put your entire balance only.)  Very important, we can't make partial withdrawals, if you want to withdraw your tokens you have to withdraw the entire balance. You can leave your tokens on ProjectArena. You, and can withdraw your balance at a later date. ( All bounty tokens will be air-dropped so please don't email us for Bounty tokens.)   If you have any other questions regarding trading or anything else you can contact us here or at contact@projectarena.io

Author: Bitsbytes
Title: [ANN] Arena - Cryptocurrency Social Network v.1 Alpha Release
Body: Arena is a cryptocurrency social media platform where members share their cryptocurrency trading ideas and predictions. Members are awarded in Arena tokens for their contributions by other members. There are also user groups, a public troll box, chatroom, and public forums. Users can easily send any other user any ERC20 token from their profile. All token transfers use a small amount of Arena token as fuel.  Like other social media platforms, members will have profiles where they can share information, links to other social media pages, and contact information.   Discord https://discord.gg/jZ4vXDP  Token information:  Total supply: 14,000,000  Token:Ethereum ERC20  ERC20 Token Address https://etherscan.io/address/0xf9c9da0c81fffd491458881410903561d1e40fd0   Trading: Arena is trading on https://forkdelta.app/#!/trade/ARENA-ETH  No inflation!  Website: https://www.arenasocial.io  Summary of Current and Future Features:  1. Advanced user profiles: (active)  2.  Donation functionality: Send Arena tokens to content creators (beta).  3. Send users Arena and ERC20 tokens (beta).  4. Site wide airdrops: Receive outside airdrops from other projects. All new airdrops will require to pay a small fee in Arena tokens as fuel (beta).  5. Advertising functionality: Purchase advertising on Arena with Arena tokens.  6. Trollbox: Chat with other members (active).  7. User groups: Join a trading user group and share your cryptocurrency trading knowledge.  Click Below to Learn More about the Arena Social Network https://arenasocial.io/2019/06/09/arena-v-1-alpha-launch/

Title: [ANN] Arena - Cryptocurrency Social Network v.1 Alpha Release
Body: This is a lot different from Wagerr. Wagerr is a betting site where people place bets. Sports picks and cryptocurrency picks will be purchased with the community token. The community token can be used for tipping other members also.
